g-offset-2" href="/entity/2746">अर्घाखाँची जिल्ला (पाणिनी गाउँपालिका वडा नं. ३), जनकपुर (प्रदेश अनुसन्धान तथा प्रशिक्षण केन्द्र), रुपन्देही जिल्ला (शुद्धोधन गाउँपालिका वडा नं. ४), भक्तपुर जिल्ला (मध्यपुर थिमि, लोकन्थली), पर्सा जिल्ला (वीरगंज)</a></div></div></div></div><div class="flex items-center p-6 mt-auto px-4 pb-4 pt-4 sm:px-5 sm:pb-5"><a class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap text-sm ring-offset-background focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:size-4 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 bg-primary text-primary-foreground font-bold shadow-lg shadow-primary/20 transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-primary/85 h-10 px-4 w-full rounded-2xl py-3" href="/case/case-081-cr-0127-b807df">विवरण हेर्नुहोस् →</a></div></div></article></div></div><div class="text-center sm:hidden mt-8"><a class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-full text-sm ring-offset-background transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:size-4 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 border border-primary font-bold bg-background text-primary hover:bg-accent hover:text-foreground h-10 px-4 py-2 w-full" href="/search">View all cases <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-right ml-2 h-4 w-4"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg></a></div></div></section><section class="relative isolate overflow-hidden border-b border-border bg-[linear-gradient(135deg,hsl(var(--primary))_0%,hsl(var(--primary))_34%,hsl(var(--accent))_100%)] py-16 dark:bg-[linear-gradient(135deg,hsl(215_70%_12%)_0%,hsl(220_38%_18%)_42%,hsl(354_66%_37%)_100%)] md:py-20"><div aria-hidden="true" class="absolute -right-20 -top-28 -z-10 h-80 w-80 rounded-full bg-secondary/30 blur-3xl"></div><div aria-hidden="true" class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_16%_20%,hsl(var(--secondary)/0.24),transparent_34%),linear-gradient(135deg,hsl(var(--primary)/0.3)_0%,transparent_48%,hsl(var(--accent)/0.2)_100%)]"></div><div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center"><div class="mx-auto flex max-w-3xl flex-col items-center"><h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold leading-tight tracking-normal text-white md:text-4xl">Know of an undocumented case?</h2><p class="mt-5 max-w-2xl text-sm leading-7 text-white/90 md:text-base">Help us hold the powerful accountable. Submit information about missing corruption cases, officials, or entities to be added to the Jawafdehi archive.</p><button class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-full text-sm ring-offset-background focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:size-4 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 transition-colors duration-200 h-11 px-8 mt-8 bg-white font-semibold text-slate-950 shadow-lg shadow-black/10 hover:bg-white/90 dark:bg-white dark:text-slate-950 dark:hover:bg-white/90" type="button" aria-haspopup="dialog" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="radix-:Ruta:" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-file-plus2 h-5 w-5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 22h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7l-5-5H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v4"></path><path d="M14 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4"></path><path d="M3 15h6"></path><path d="M6 12v6"></path></svg>Report a Case</button></div></div></section><section id="faq" class="bg-background py-12 md:py-16" aria-labelledby="faq-title"><div class="container mx-auto grid gap-8 px-4 md:grid-cols-[minmax(0,0.9fr)_minmax(0,1.45fr)] md:items-start md:gap-12 lg:gap-16"><div class="max-w-md"><h2 id="faq-title" class="max-w-sm text-3xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-normal text-primary md:text-4xl">बारम्बार सोधिने प्रश्नहरू</h2><p class="mt-5 text-sm leading-7 text-foreground/60 md:text-base">जवाफदेहीबारे तपाईंका महत्त्वपूर्ण प्रश्नहरूको उत्तर यहाँ संकलन गरेका छौं।</p></div><ul class="flex flex-col gap-2.5"><li class="group overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-border/70 bg-card text-card-foreground shadow-sm shadow-foreground/5 outline-none backdrop-blur-[12px] transition-[background-color,border-color,box-shadow,transform] duration-300 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-foreground/15 hover:bg-card hover:text-card-foreground hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-foreground/10 focus-visible:-translate-y-0.5 focus-visible:border-foreground/15 focus-visible:bg-card focus-visible:text-card-foreground focus-visible:shadow-md focus-visible:shadow-foreground/10 focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-background focus-within:-translate-y-0.5 focus-within:border-foreground/15 focus-within:bg-card focus-within:text-card-foreground focus-within:shadow-md focus-within:shadow-foreground/10 motion-reduce:transform-none motion-reduce:transition-none"><button type="button" class="w-full text-left" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-how-to-report-answer"><div class="flex min-h-12 items-center justify-between gap-4 px-4 py-3.5"><h3 id="faq-how-to-report-question" class="text-left text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-foreground transition-colors duration-200 group-hover:text-primary group-focus-visible:text-primary group-focus-within:text-primary md:text-base">म भ्रष्टाचारको मुद्दा कसरी रिपोर्ट गर्न सक्छु?</h3><span class="relative flex h-7 w-7 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-border/70 bg-background/70 text-foreground/50 shadow-sm shadow-foreground/5 transition-[background-color,border-color,color] duration-200 group-hover:border-accent/20 group-hover:bg-accent/10 group-hover:text-accent group-focus-visible:border-accent/20 group-focus-visible:bg-accent/10 group-focus-within:border-accent/20 group-focus-within:bg-accent/10 group-focus-within:text-accent motion-reduce:transition-none" aria-hidden="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus absolute h-3.5 w-3.5 transition-all duration-300 ease-out group-hover:rotate-90 group-hover:scale-[0.82] group-hover:opacity-0 group-focus-visible:rotate-90 group-focus-visible:scale-[0.82] group-focus-visible:opacity-0 group-focus-within:rotate-90 group-focus-within:scale-[0.82] group-focus-within:opacity-0 motion-reduce:transition-none"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5v14"></path></svg><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-minus absolute h-3.5 w-3.5 -rotate-90 scale-[0.82] opacity-0 transition-all duration-300 ease-out group-hover:rotate-0 group-hover:scale-100 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-visible:rotate-0 group-focus-visible:scale-100 group-focus-visible:opacity-100 group-focus-within:rotate-0 group-focus-within:scale-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 motion-reduce:transition-none"><path d="M5 12h14"></path></svg></span></div></button><div id="faq-how-to-report-answer" class="max-h-0 -translate-y-1 overflow-hidden opacity-0 transition-[max-height,opacity,transform] duration-300 ease-out group-hover:max-h-96 group-hover:translate-y-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-visible:max-h-96 group-focus-visible:translate-y-0 group-focus-visible:opacity-100 group-focus-within:max-h-96 group-focus-within:translate-y-0 group-focus-within:opacity-100 motion-reduce:transform-none motion-reduce:transition-none"><div class="space-y-3 px-4 pb-4 pr-12 text-sm leading-6 text-muted-foreground md:text-base"><p>तपाईं हाम्रो &quot;आरोप रिपोर्ट गर्नुहोस्&quot; फर्म मार्फत मुद्दा रिपोर्ट गर्न सक्नुहुन्छ। कृपया सम्भव भएसम्म विस्तृत विवरण र समर्थन दस्तावेजीकरण प्रदान गर्नुहोस्। तपाईंले गुमनाम वा आफ्नो पहिचानसँग पेश गर्न छान्न सक्नुहुन्छ।</p><p>सबै पेशहरू प्रकाशन अघि हाम्रो मध्यस्थता टोलीद्वारा समीक्षा गरिन्छ। यदि आवश्यक छ भने हामी थप प्रमाणीकरणको लागि तपाईंसँग सम्पर्क गर्न सक्छौं।</p></div></div></li><li class="group overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-border/70 bg-card text-card-foreground shadow-sm shadow-foreground/5 outline-none backdrop-blur-[12px] transition-[background-color,border-color,box-shadow,transform] duration-300 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-foreground/15 hover:bg-card hover:text-card-foreground hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-foreground/10 focus-visible:-translate-y-0.5 focus-visible:border-foreground/15 focus-visible:bg-card focus-visible:text-card-foreground focus-visible:shadow-md focus-visible:shadow-foreground/10 focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-background focus-within:-translate-y-0.5 focus-within:border-foreground/15 focus-within:bg-card focus-within:text-card-foreground focus-within:shadow-md focus-within:shadow-foreground/10 motion-reduce:transform-none motion-reduce:transition-none"><button type="button" class="w-full text-left" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-after-submit-answer"><div class="flex min-h-12 items-center justify-between gap-4 px-4 py-3.5"><h3 id="faq-after-submit-question" class="text-left text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-foreground transition-colors duration-200 group-hover:text-primary group-focus-visible:text-primary group-focus-within:text-primary md:text-base">मैले रिपोर्ट पेश गरेपछि के हुन्छ?</h3><span class="relative flex h-7 w-7 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-border/70 bg-background/70 text-foreground/50 shadow-sm shadow-foreground/5 transition-[background-color,border-color,color] duration-200 group-hover:border-accent/20 group-hover:bg-accent/10 group-hover:text-accent group-focus-visible:border-accent/20 group-focus-visible:bg-accent/10 group-focus-within:border-accent/20 group-focus-within:bg-accent/10 group-focus-within:text-accent motion-reduce:transition-none" aria-hidden="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus absolute h-3.5 w-3.5 transition-all duration-300 ease-out group-hover:rotate-90 group-hover:scale-[0.82] group-hover:opacity-0 group-focus-visible:rotate-90 group-focus-visible:scale-[0.82] group-focus-visible:opacity-0 group-focus-within:rotate-90 group-focus-within:scale-[0.82] group-focus-within:opacity-0 motion-reduce:transition-none"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5v14"></path></svg><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-minus absolute h-3.5 w-3.5 -rotate-90 scale-[0.82] opacity-0 transition-all duration-300 ease-out group-hover:rotate-0 group-hover:scale-100 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-visible:rotate-0 group-focus-visible:scale-100 group-focus-visible:opacity-100 group-focus-within:rotate-0 group-focus-within:scale-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 motion-reduce:transition-none"><path d="M5 12h14"></path></svg></span></div></button><div id="faq-after-submit-answer" class="max-h-0 -translate-y-1 overflow-hidden opacity-0 transition-[max-height,opacity,transform] duration-300 ease-out group-hover:max-h-96 group-hover:translate-y-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-visible:max-h-96 group-focus-visible:translate-y-0 group-focus-visible:opacity-100 group-focus-within:max-h-96 group-focus-within:translate-y-0 group-focus-within:opacity-100 motion-reduce:transform-none motion-reduce:transition-none"><div class="space-y-3 px-4 pb-4 pr-12 text-sm leading-6 text-muted-foreground md:text-base"><p>तपाईंको पेश हाम्रो प्रमाणीकरण क्यूमा जान्छ। हाम्रो टोलीले जानकारी समीक्षा गर्छ, धेरै स्रोतहरू मार्फत प्रमाणित गर्छ र यो हाम्रो प्रकाशन मानकहरू पूरा गर्छ वा छैन भनेर निर्धारण गर्छ। यो प्रक्रिया सामान्यतया मुद्दा जटिलतामा निर्भर गरेर 7-14 दिन लिन्छ। यदि तपाईंले सम्पर्क जानकारी प्रदान गर्नुभयो भने तपाईंलाई नतीजाको बारेमा सूचना दिइनेछ।</p></div></div></li><li class="group overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-border/70 bg-card text-card-foreground shadow-sm shadow-foreground/5 outline-none backdrop-blur-[12px] transition-[background-color,border-color,box-shadow,transform] duration-300 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-foreground/15 hover:bg-card hover:text-card-foreground hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-foreground/10 focus-visible:-translate-y-0.5 focus-visible:border-foreground/15 focus-visible:bg-card focus-visible:text-card-foreground focus-visible:shadow-md focus-visible:shadow-foreground/10 focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-background focus-within:-translate-y-0.5 focus-within:border-foreground/15 focus-within:bg-card focus-within:text-card-foreground focus-within:shadow-md focus-within:shadow-foreground/10 motion-reduce:transform-none motion-reduce:transition-none"><button type="button" class="w-full text-left" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-anonymous-answer"><div class="flex min-h-12 items-center justify-between gap-4 px-4 py-3.5"><h3 id="faq-anonymous-question" class="text-left text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-foreground transition-colors duration-200 group-hover:text-primary group-focus-visible:text-primary group-focus-within:text-primary md:text-base">यदि मैले गुमनाम रिपोर्ट गर्छु भने मेरो पहिचान सुरक्षित छ?</h3><span class="relative flex h-7 w-7 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-border/70 bg-background/70 text-foreground/50 shadow-sm shadow-foreground/5 transition-[background-color,border-color,color] duration-200 group-hover:border-accent/20 group-hover:bg-accent/10 group-hover:text-accent group-focus-visible:border-accent/20 group-focus-visible:bg-accent/10 group-focus-within:border-accent/20 group-focus-within:bg-accent/10 group-focus-within:text-accent motion-reduce:transition-none" aria-hidden="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus absolute h-3.5 w-3.5 transition-all duration-300 ease-out group-hover:rotate-90 group-hover:scale-[0.82] group-hover:opacity-0 group-focus-visible:rotate-90 group-focus-visible:scale-[0.82] group-focus-visible:opacity-0 group-focus-within:rotate-90 group-focus-within:scale-[0.82] group-focus-within:opacity-0 motion-reduce:transition-none"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5v14"></path></svg><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-minus absolute h-3.5 w-3.5 -rotate-90 scale-[0.82] opacity-0 transition-all duration-300 ease-out group-hover:rotate-0 group-hover:scale-100 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-visible:rotate-0 group-focus-visible:scale-100 group-focus-visible:opacity-100 group-focus-within:rotate-0 group-focus-within:scale-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 motion-reduce:transition-none"><path d="M5 12h14"></path></svg></span></div></button><div id="faq-anonymous-answer" class="max-h-0 -translate-y-1 overflow-hidden opacity-0 transition-[max-height,opacity,transform] duration-300 ease-out group-hover:max-h-96 group-hover:translate-y-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-visible:max-h-96 group-focus-visible:translate-y-0 group-focus-visible:opacity-100 group-focus-within:max-h-96 group-focus-within:translate-y-0 group-focus-within:opacity-100 motion-reduce:transform-none motion-reduce:transition-none"><div class="space-y-3 px-4 pb-4 pr-12 text-sm leading-6 text-muted-foreground md:text-base"><p>हो। हामी योगदानकर्ता गोपनीयतालाई गम्भीरतापूर्वक लिन्छौं। गुमनाम पेशहरूले कुनै पहिचान जानकारी भण्डारण गर्दैन र हामीसँग सबै योगदानकर्ताहरूलाई प्रतिशोधबाट सुरक्षा गर्ने उपायहरू छन्। फोन नम्बरहरू र राष्ट्रिय ID नम्बरहरू जस्ता व्यक्तिगत डाटा कहिल्यै प्रकाशित हुँदैन।</p></div></div></li><li class="group overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-border/70 bg-card text-card-foreground shadow-sm shadow-foreground/5 outline-none backdrop-blur-[12px] transition-[background-color,border-color,box-shadow,transform] duration-300 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-foreground/15 hover:bg-card hover:text-card-foreground hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-foreground/10 focus-visible:-translate-y-0.5 focus-visible:border-foreground/15 focus-visible:bg-card focus-visible:text-card-foreground focus-visible:shadow-md focus-visible:shadow-foreground/10 focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-background focus-within:-translate-y-0.5 focus-within:border-foreground/15 focus-within:bg-card focus-within:text-card-foreground focus-within:shadow-md focus-within:shadow-foreground/10 motion-reduce:transform-none motion-reduce:transition-none"><button type="button" class="w-full text-left" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-entity-response-answer"><div class="flex min-h-12 items-center justify-between gap-4 px-4 py-3.5"><h3 id="faq-entity-response-question" class="text-left text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-foreground transition-colors duration-200 group-hover:text-primary group-focus-visible:text-primary group-focus-within:text-primary md:text-base">के आरोपित एकाइहरूले आरोपहरूको जवाफ दिन सक्छन्?</h3><span class="relative flex h-7 w-7 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-border/70 bg-background/70 text-foreground/50 shadow-sm shadow-foreground/5 transition-[background-color,border-color,color] duration-200 group-hover:border-accent/20 group-hover:bg-accent/10 group-hover:text-accent group-focus-visible:border-accent/20 group-focus-visible:bg-accent/10 group-focus-within:border-accent/20 group-focus-within:bg-accent/10 group-focus-within:text-accent motion-reduce:transition-none" aria-hidden="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus absolute h-3.5 w-3.5 transition-all duration-300 ease-out group-hover:rotate-90 group-hover:scale-[0.82] group-hover:opacity-0 group-focus-visible:rotate-90 group-focus-visible:scale-[0.82] group-focus-visible:opacity-0 group-focus-within:rotate-90 group-focus-within:scale-[0.82] group-focus-within:opacity-0 motion-reduce:transition-none"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5v14"></path></svg><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-minus absolute h-3.5 w-3.5 -rotate-90 scale-[0.82] opacity-0 transition-all duration-300 ease-out group-hover:rotate-0 group-hover:scale-100 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-visible:rotate-0 group-focus-visible:scale-100 group-focus-visible:opacity-100 group-focus-within:rotate-0 group-focus-within:scale-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 motion-reduce:transition-none"><path d="M5 12h14"></path></svg></span></div></button><div id="faq-entity-response-answer" class="max-h-0 -translate-y-1 overflow-hidden opacity-0 transition-[max-height,opacity,transform] duration-300 ease-out group-hover:max-h-96 group-hover:translate-y-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-visible:max-h-96 group-focus-visible:translate-y-0 group-focus-visible:opacity-100 group-focus-within:max-h-96 group-focus-within:translate-y-0 group-focus-within:opacity-100 motion-reduce:transform-none motion-reduce:transition-none"><div class="space-y-3 px-4 pb-4 pr-12 text-sm leading-6 text-muted-foreground md:text-base"><p>निश्चित रूपमा। हामी निष्पक्ष प्रतिनिधित्वमा विश्वास गर्छौं। आरोपित व्यक्तिहरू र एकाइहरूले हाम्रो &quot;संस्था प्रतिक्रिया&quot; पोर्टल मार्फत प्रतिक्रियाहरू पेश गर्न सक्छन्। यी प्रतिक्रियाहरू प्रामाणिकताको लागि प्रमाणित गरिन्छ र पूर्ण सन्दर्भ प्रदान गर्न आरोपहरूसँगै प्रकाशित गरिन्छ।</p></div></div></li><li class="group overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-border/70 bg-card text-card-foreground shadow-sm shadow-foreground/5 outline-none backdrop-blur-[12px] transition-[background-color,border-color,box-shadow,transform] duration-300 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-foreground/15 hover:bg-card hover:text-card-foreground hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-foreground/10 focus-visible:-translate-y-0.5 focus-visible:border-foreground/15 focus-visible:bg-card focus-visible:text-card-foreground focus-visible:shadow-md focus-visible:shadow-foreground/10 focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-background focus-within:-translate-y-0.5 focus-within:border-foreground/15 focus-within:bg-card focus-within:text-card-foreground focus-within:shadow-md focus-within:shadow-foreground/10 motion-reduce:transform-none motion-reduce:transition-none"><button type="button" class="w-full text-left" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-inaccurate-answer"><div class="flex min-h-12 items-center justify-between gap-4 px-4 py-3.5"><h3 id="faq-inaccurate-question" class="text-left text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-foreground transition-colors duration-200 group-hover:text-primary group-focus-visible:text-primary group-focus-within:text-primary md:text-base">यदि प्लेटफर्ममा जानकारी गलत छ भने के हुन्छ?</h3><span class="relative flex h-7 w-7 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-border/70 bg-background/70 text-foreground/50 shadow-sm shadow-foreground/5 transition-[background-color,border-color,color] duration-200 group-hover:border-accent/20 group-hover:bg-accent/10 group-hover:text-accent group-focus-visible:border-accent/20 group-focus-visible:bg-accent/10 group-focus-within:border-accent/20 group-focus-within:bg-accent/10 group-focus-within:text-accent motion-reduce:transition-none" aria-hidden="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus absolute h-3.5 w-3.5 transition-all duration-300 ease-out group-hover:rotate-90 group-hover:scale-[0.82] group-hover:opacity-0 group-focus-visible:rotate-90 group-focus-visible:scale-[0.82] group-focus-visible:opacity-0 group-focus-within:rotate-90 group-focus-within:scale-[0.82] group-focus-within:opacity-0 motion-reduce:transition-none"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5v14"></path></svg><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-minus absolute h-3.5 w-3.5 -rotate-90 scale-[0.82] opacity-0 transition-all duration-300 ease-out group-hover:rotate-0 group-hover:scale-100 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-visible:rotate-0 group-focus-visible:scale-100 group-focus-visible:opacity-100 group-focus-within:rotate-0 group-focus-within:scale-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 motion-reduce:transition-none"><path d="M5 12h14"></path></svg></span></div></button><div id="faq-inaccurate-answer" class="max-h-0 -translate-y-1 overflow-hidden opacity-0 transition-[max-height,opacity,transform] duration-300 ease-out group-hover:max-h-96 group-hover:translate-y-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-visible:max-h-96 group-focus-visible:translate-y-0 group-focus-visible:opacity-100 group-focus-within:max-h-96 group-focus-within:translate-y-0 group-focus-within:opacity-100 motion-reduce:transform-none motion-reduce:transition-none"><div class="space-y-3 px-4 pb-4 pr-12 text-sm leading-6 text-muted-foreground md:text-base"><p>हाम्रो कडा प्रमाणीकरण प्रक्रिया बावजुद, त्रुटिहरू हुन सक्छन्। यदि तपाईंले गलत जानकारी फेला पार्नुभयो भने, कृपया समर्थन प्रमाणको साथ हाम्रो प्रतिक्रिया फर्म मार्फत तुरुन्तै हामीसँग सम्पर्क गर्नुहोस्। हामी कुनै पनि प्रमाणित अशुद्धिहरूको समीक्षा र सुधार तुरुन्तै गर्नेछौं। सबै सुधारहरू मुद्दाको लेखापरीक्षा ट्र्याकमा दस्तावेजीकृत गरिन्छ।</p></div></div></li><li class="group overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-border/70 bg-card text-card-foreground shadow-sm shadow-foreground/5 outline-none backdrop-blur-[12px] transition-[background-color,border-color,box-shadow,transform] duration-300 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-foreground/15 hover:bg-card hover:text-card-foreground hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-foreground/10 focus-visible:-translate-y-0.5 focus-visible:border-foreground/15 focus-visible:bg-card focus-visible:text-card-foreground focus-visible:shadow-md focus-visible:shadow-foreground/10 focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-background focus-within:-translate-y-0.5 focus-within:border-foreground/15 focus-within:bg-card focus-within:text-card-foreground focus-within:shadow-md focus-within:shadow-foreground/10 motion-reduce:transform-none motion-reduce:transition-none"><button type="button" class="w-full text-left" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-funding-answer"><div class="flex min-h-12 items-center justify-between gap-4 px-4 py-3.5"><h3 id="faq-funding-question" class="text-left text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-foreground transition-colors duration-200 group-hover:text-primary group-focus-visible:text-primary group-focus-within:text-primary md:text-base">यो प्लेटफर्म कसरी वित्तपोषित छ?</h3><span class="relative flex h-7 w-7 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-border/70 bg-background/70 text-foreground/50 shadow-sm shadow-foreground/5 transition-[background-color,border-color,color] duration-200 group-hover:border-accent/20 group-hover:bg-accent/10 group-hover:text-accent group-focus-visible:border-accent/20 group-focus-visible:bg-accent/10 group-focus-within:border-accent/20 group-focus-within:bg-accent/10 group-focus-within:text-accent motion-reduce:transition-none" aria-hidden="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus absolute h-3.5 w-3.5 transition-all duration-300 ease-out group-hover:rotate-90 group-hover:scale-[0.82] group-hover:opacity-0 group-focus-visible:rotate-90 group-focus-visible:scale-[0.82] group-focus-visible:opacity-0 group-focus-within:rotate-90 group-focus-within:scale-[0.82] group-focus-within:opacity-0 motion-reduce:transition-none"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5v14"></path></svg><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-minus absolute h-3.5 w-3.5 -rotate-90 scale-[0.82] opacity-0 transition-all duration-300 ease-out group-hover:rotate-0 group-hover:scale-100 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-visible:rotate-0 group-focus-visible:scale-100 group-focus-visible:opacity-100 group-focus-within:rotate-0 group-focus-within:scale-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 motion-reduce:transition-none"><path d="M5 12h14"></path></svg></span></div></button><div id="faq-funding-answer" class="max-h-0 -translate-y-1 overflow-hidden opacity-0 transition-[max-height,opacity,transform] duration-300 ease-out group-hover:max-h-96 group-hover:translate-y-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-visible:max-h-96 group-focus-visible:translate-y-0 group-focus-visible:opacity-100 group-focus-within:max-h-96 group-focus-within:translate-y-0 group-focus-within:opacity-100 motion-reduce:transform-none motion-reduce:transition-none"><div class="space-y-3 px-4 pb-4 pr-12 text-sm leading-6 text-muted-foreground md:text-base"><p>सार्वजनिक जवाफदेहिता प्लेटफर्म नागरिक एकाइहरूसँग साझेदारी र पारदर्शिता-केन्द्रित एकाइहरूबाट सम्भावित अनुदानहरू मार्फत वित्तपोषित छ। हामी सम्पादकीय स्वतन्त्रता कायम राख्छौं र सरकारी एकाइहरू वा एकाइहरूबाट वित्तपोषण स्वीकार गर्दैनौं जसले हाम्रो अखण्डतालाई समझौता गर्न सक्छ।</p></div></div></li><li class="group overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-border/70 bg-card text-card-foreground shadow-sm shadow-foreground/5 outline-none backdrop-blur-[12px] transition-[background-color,border-color,box-shadow,transform] duration-300 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-foreground/15 hover:bg-card hover:text-card-foreground hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-foreground/10 focus-visible:-translate-y-0.5 focus-visible:border-foreground/15 focus-visible:bg-card focus-visible:text-card-foreground focus-visible:shadow-md focus-visible:shadow-foreground/10 focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-background focus-within:-translate-y-0.5 focus-within:border-foreground/15 focus-within:bg-card focus-within:text-card-foreground focus-within:shadow-md focus-within:shadow-foreground/10 motion-reduce:transform-none motion-reduce:transition-none"><button type="button" class="w-full text-left" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-use-info-answer"><div class="flex min-h-12 items-center justify-between gap-4 px-4 py-3.5"><h3 id="faq-use-info-question" class="text-left text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-foreground transition-colors duration-200 group-hover:text-primary group-focus-visible:text-primary group-focus-within:text-primary md:text-base">के मैले यस प्लेटफर्मबाट जानकारी प्रयोग गर्न सक्छु?</h3><span class="relative flex h-7 w-7 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-border/70 bg-background/70 text-foreground/50 shadow-sm shadow-foreground/5 transition-[background-color,border-color,color] duration-200 group-hover:border-accent/20 group-hover:bg-accent/10 group-hover:text-accent group-focus-visible:border-accent/20 group-focus-visible:bg-accent/10 group-focus-within:border-accent/20 group-focus-within:bg-accent/10 group-focus-within:text-accent motion-reduce:transition-none" aria-hidden="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus absolute h-3.5 w-3.5 transition-all duration-300 ease-out group-hover:rotate-90 group-hover:scale-[0.82] group-hover:opacity-0 group-focus-visible:rotate-90 group-focus-visible:scale-[0.82] group-focus-visible:opacity-0 group-focus-within:rotate-90 group-focus-within:scale-[0.82] group-focus-within:opacity-0 motion-reduce:transition-none"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5v14"></path></svg><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-minus absolute h-3.5 w-3.5 -rotate-90 scale-[0.82] opacity-0 transition-all duration-300 ease-out group-hover:rotate-0 group-hover:scale-100 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-visible:rotate-0 group-focus-visible:scale-100 group-focus-visible:opacity-100 group-focus-within:rotate-0 group-focus-within:scale-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 motion-reduce:transition-none"><path d="M5 12h14"></path></svg></span></div></button><div id="faq-use-info-answer" class="max-h-0 -translate-y-1 overflow-hidden opacity-0 transition-[max-height,opacity,transform] duration-300 ease-out group-hover:max-h-96 group-hover:translate-y-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-visible:max-h-96 group-focus-visible:translate-y-0 group-focus-visible:opacity-100 group-focus-within:max-h-96 group-focus-within:translate-y-0 group-focus-within:opacity-100 motion-reduce:transform-none motion-reduce:transition-none"><div class="space-y-3 px-4 pb-4 pr-12 text-sm leading-6 text-muted-foreground md:text-base"><p>हो! यस प्लेटफर्ममा सबै जानकारी सार्वजनिक रूपमा पहुँचयोग्य छ र अनुसन्धान, पत्रकारिता, वकालत वा शैक्षिक उद्देश्यहरूको लागि स्वतन्त्र रूपमा प्रयोग गर्न सकिन्छ। हामी उचित उल्लेख र डाटाको जिम्मेवार प्रयोगलाई प्रोत्साहन गर्छौं।</p></div></div></li></ul></div></section><section aria-labelledby="supporting-partners-title" class="bg-background py-10 md:py-12"><div class="container mx-auto flex flex-col items-center px-4"><h2 id="supporting-partners-title" class="text-center text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-accent">Supporting Partners</h2><a href="https://monal.cloud" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Visit Monal Cloud"><img src="/assets/monal.svg" alt="Monal" class="h-24 w-auto object-contain"/></a></div></section></main></div></main><footer class="relative isolate overflow-hidden border-t bg-[var(--footer-bg)] text-[var(--footer-fg)] [--footer-bg:hsl(var(--primary))] [--footer-fg:hsl(var(--primary-foreground))] [--footer-muted:hsl(var(--primary-foreground)/0.78)] [--footer-title:hsl(354_100%_71%)] [--footer-soft:hsl(var(--primary-foreground)/0.10)] [--footer-soft-hover:hsl(var(--primary-foreground)/0.16)] [--footer-border:hsl(var(--primary-foreground)/0.16)] [--footer-border-hover:hsl(var(--primary-foreground)/0.28)] [--footer-dot:hsl(var(--primary-foreground)/0.30)] border-[var(--footer-border)] dark:[--footer-bg:hsl(var(--card))] dark:[--footer-fg:hsl(var(--card-foreground))] dark:[--footer-muted:hsl(var(--card-foreground)/0.82)] dark:[--footer-soft:hsl(var(--backgro